2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn28g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=8252b3d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）"},{"pid":"73876b17b75f518566440d3551bbcb5aa3b3e7eb","tid":1351170,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"a2f9eac80ab4250939282d06ad4081ec8dbd24e5","tid":1351170,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f4075d1b16623ed5fab04453239e3691805d8fa","tid":1351170,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"上環個班收到風呀<br />\n無受傷 仲行得走得既<br />\n都即刻衝去元朗<br />\n仲要搵車一齊入元朗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好白費佢地心機啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry